FBIS4-59481 "drnes094dd_94007" FBIS-NES-94-094 Daily Report 14 May 1994 Palestinian Affairs Appointment of Security Head Announced Appointment of Security Head Announced LD1405181094 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 14 May 94 LD1405181094 Algiers Voice of Palestine Arabic BFN [Excerpt] It has been announced today that President Yasir 'Arafat had issued a decision on 10 December 1993 which stipulated the appointment of Major-General (Musbah Hanafi Saqr) director of preventive security. WAFA learned that this decision was not made public at the time to protect the secret presence of brother Major-General Saqr in the occupied Palestinian territories, whereby his martyrdom was announced in 1968 in order to protect the secrecy and continuation of his work. [passage omitted]
